             (:domain "π_5 projection" :code "(define (pi5 t) (list-ref t 4))"))
     :explanation "In list, fifth names position 5. On a rig, the fifth wheel is the named coupling point. In math, π_5 projects the fifth coordinate. All three share: named handle for canonical position 5."
     :meta "The shape transfers where position 5 has stable meaning."))
